            "date": "2010-08-10 21:51:00", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "As I have pointed out before, this feature is essentially useless:\r MakeOwner= attacker // normal // neutral // random\r\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\"attacker\" is the unit firing the weapon.\r", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "[...]\r\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\"normal\" is the unit firing the weapon. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "[...]\r\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\"neutral\" and \"random\" should be self-explanatory.\r", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "So basically, you have 4 cases - two of which are identical and do exactly the same as mind control in its various forms, one which does essentially the same as KillDriver, and one which, as Blade pointed out, is partially similar to the chaos effect and practically silly and without a decent, remotely common usage case.\r", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "It's a pointless request with little practical value [...]\r\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Add to that that there has been no active interest in this issue since the day after its submission, and even on that day, it was to defend the issue against accusations of worthlessness, and to point out semi-duplicates, and there simply doesn't seem much point in implementing this.\r", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "The issue will stay un-closed for a little while, so if you can provide a common, widely-used usage case that cannot possibly be done through YR's/Ares's existing mind control, KillDriver, Engineer or VehicleThief functions, we'll gladly reconsider, but for the moment, this request looks superfluous and we're rejecting it.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }
            ], 
